580
00:27:02,100 --> 00:27:04,320
You left a smile in my heart.

581
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:06,840
I don’t ask for much.

582
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:08,000
As long as there’s a corner

583
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,880
for me to lay my eyes

584
00:27:09,880 --> 00:27:11,340
on you with my deepest love.

585
00:27:11,340 --> 00:27:12,320
A memory which I’ll never

586
00:27:12,320 --> 00:27:14,400
regret for the rest of my life.

587
00:27:15,320 --> 00:27:16,840
I’d like to give this medal

588
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:17,720
to the person I love.

589
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:24,920
My dearest father, Principle Shi.

590
00:27:31,640 --> 00:27:32,560
Son.

591
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:37,160
You are my dearest son.

592
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,760
Is that so funny?

593
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:44,800
