596
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,160
Good for you.

597
00:28:04,960 --> 00:28:05,920
Lift your arms.

598
00:28:15,360 --> 00:28:17,440
No matter what,

599
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,520
