647
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:58,240
It’s the past.

648
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,240
Let’s forget it.

649
00:31:00,560 --> 00:31:01,480
Aren’t

650
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,360
