651
00:31:04,760 --> 00:31:06,640
I don’t get mad so easily.

652
00:31:06,640 --> 00:31:08,080
If I was always mad,

653
00:31:08,080 --> 00:31:09,800
I would have been mad
at Miao for millions of times.

654
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:13,960
Here. Eat some vegetables.

655
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,600
Have a rib.

656
00:31:25,120 --> 00:31:25,760
Is it good?

657
00:31:27,640 --> 00:31:29,400
Not as special as Aunt Fang’s cooking.

658
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:33,080
The ribs cooked by her

659
