664
00:31:51,080 --> 00:31:51,880
I remember, too.

665
00:31:53,160 --> 00:31:54,440
That was

666
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:56,360
the first time I went to your home.

667
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:59,880
Lu Miao was sitting next to me.

668
00:31:59,880 --> 00:32:01,280
She was curious about my artificial leg
when I came in.

669
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:03,520
She wanted

670
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:05,520
to have a same one as mine.

671
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:08,760
I was so mad

672
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:09,800
that I pounded the desk

673
00:32:09,800 --> 00:32:10,720
so hard with the chopstick

674
00:32:10,720 --> 00:32:11,520
in my hand.

675
00:32:12,760 --> 00:32:13,760
Then it occurred

676
00:32:14,280 --> 00:32:16,640
to me that she was just a kid.

677
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:18,720
Miao was very upset, too.

678
00:32:19,320 --> 00:32:21,160
She asked me later

679
00:32:21,160 --> 00:32:22,680
how come

680
00:32:22,680 --> 00:32:24,480
you could be the RoboCop

681
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,800
but not her.

682
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:29,680
And if she was ignored by God.

683
00:32:29,680 --> 00:32:31,000
That’s really her style.

684
00:32:35,480 --> 00:32:36,800
Jiang.

685
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,960
