for dinner for long.

686
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,200
Come again someday.

687
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,120
Tell me whatever you want to eat.

688
00:32:42,120 --> 00:32:43,760
Aunt Fang and I will cook for you.

689
00:32:46,880 --> 00:32:47,600
Okay.

690
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:52,600
Are you still yearning
for ribs cooked by her?

691
00:32:52,600 --> 00:32:53,120
Yes.

692
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:56,720
Alright.

